net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base.datatype.adapter.jackson

Class EnumTypeJsonDeserializer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonDeserializer<T>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base.datatype.adapter.jackson.EnumTypeJsonDeserializer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the generic type of the Datatype to serialize.

    public class EnumTypeJsonDeserializer<T>
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonDeserializer<T>
    This is a generic implementation of JsonDeserializer based on EnumProvider so every Enum and EnumType supported by EnumProvider can be deserialized from JSON.
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
    See Also:
    DatatypeJsonSerializer
